snippet.title: Connect - Android Application from AppSoGreat
snippet.description:
Connect all the pairs. Funny and stimulating game.
http://www.appsogreat.com
  - 9 gravity modes
  - 2 themes: Abstract or Sport
  - 3 grid sizes
 
How to play?
  - Remove 2 cards with the same design that you can connect
  - If you are stuck, let's shuffle the cards
  - With timer: remove all cards in the time allotted

Try it now: https://play.google.com/store/apps/developer?id=AppSoGreat
